snippet.title: Excel Movies
snippet.description:
This is the official YouTube channel of Excel Entertainment, a film production house founded in 1999 by Ritesh Sidhwani and Farhan Akhtar. 

Excel Entertainment has produced both critically acclaimed and commercially successful films, including national award winning films like Dil Chahta Hai and Rock On. 

With films like Gully Boy, Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara, The Fukrey series, The Don series, Raees, Dil Dhadakne Do, Lakshya, Gold and Talaash among others, the production house has carved its own identity in the Indian film industry. 

Gully Boy, released in 2019, went on to win numerous awards and was also India’s official entry to the 92nd Academy Awards. 

Excel Entertainment ventured into the OTT space in 2017 with the International Emmy nominated sports drama series Inside Edge, followed by Mirzapur and Made In Heaven. 

Subscribe to Excel Movies for wholesome entertainment and latest videos from our films and shows.
